@ModularMonolithDemo_HostAddress = http://localhost:5288

### Create a product (Catalog module)
POST {{ModularMonolithDemo_HostAddress}}/catalog/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mechanical Keyboard",
  "price": 89.99,
  "stockQuantity": 10
}

### List products (Catalog module)
GET {{ModularMonolithDemo_HostAddress}}/catalog/products
Accept: application/json

### Place an order (Ordering module — reserves stock via Catalog's IProductCatalog contract)
POST {{ModularMonolithDemo_HostAddress}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lines": [
    { "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000", "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### List orders (Ordering module)
GET {{ModularMonolithDemo_HostAddress}}/orders
Accept: application/json
